&%\"xG\"\"\"F&!\"\"F&,&F%F&F&F&F&" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
55 "It factored p2 where x->x^2-1, hence it factored x^2-1." }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 10 "expand(%);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 
"" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,&*$)%\"xG\"\"#\"\"\"F(F(!\"\"" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 57 "Expand command means multiply the prior factors to
gether." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 11 "solve(%=0);" }}
{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$\"\"\"!\"\"" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "
" {TEXT -1 56 "Solve made x^2-1 =0 and gives the roots of the equation
." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 13 "fsolve(%%=0);" }}
{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$$!+++++5!\"*$\"\"\"\"\"!" }}}{EXCHG 
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 109 "As before x^2-1=0 but fsolve finds the a
pproximate root using the floating point to give a near exact number.
" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 12 "solve(p2=0);" }}{PARA 
11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#\"\"!" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
76 "p2 is an operation when this is set to equal zero, anything to zer
o is zero." }}}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 
