\"\"#,$F#!\"\"" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 84 " The equatin is
 x^2-1=2 when this is solved for the roots we see the sq rt of +or-3.
" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 13 "fsolve(p1=2);" }}{PARA 
11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$$!+330K<!\"*$\"+330K<F%" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 91 "When we solve for the floating point root we see t
