" {MPLTEXT 1 0 12 "solve(p2=2);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#\"
\"#" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 42 "When p2 is set to 2 you so
